  <h1 id="Microsoft_Xna_Framework_GraphicsDeviceManager_SynchronizeWithVerticalRetrace_" data-uid="Microsoft.Xna.Framework.GraphicsDeviceManager.SynchronizeWithVerticalRetrace*" class="text-break">GraphicsDeviceManager.SynchronizeWithVerticalRetrace Property</h1>

