    <div class="markdown level0 summary"><p>Indicates the desire for vsync when presenting the back buffer.</p>
</div>
    <div class="markdown level0 conceptual"></div>
    
      
        <div class="codewrapper">
          <pre><code class="lang-csharp hljs">public bool SynchronizeWithVerticalRetrace { get; set; }</code></pre>
        </div>
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
    
    <h id="Microsoft_Xna_Framework_GraphicsDeviceManager_SynchronizeWithVerticalRetrace_remarks">Remarks</h>
    <div class="markdown level0 remarks"><p>Vsync limits the frame rate of the game to the monitor referesh rate to prevent screen tearing.
When called at startup this will automatically set the vsync mode during initialization.  If
set after startup you must call ApplyChanges() for the vsync mode to be changed.</p>
</div>
    
    
    
    

